=== The Gradient ===

--- pure function ---
  double: (Int) -> Int
   1. add `with Pure` -> memoization, parallelism, compile-time eval
   start with (1).

--- effectful function ---
  logger: (?3) -> ?3 with Log
   1. add `with !Alloc` -> real-time safe, embeddable
   2. add `with !Network` -> sandboxed
   start with (1).

--- already annotated ---
suggestions: 0

--- multiple functions ---
  compose: (Int) -> Int
   1. add `with Pure` -> memoization, parallelism, compile-time eval
   start with (1).

--- handler absorption path ---
  processor: (Int) -> Int with Alloc
   1. wrap Alloc calls in handler
   2. add `with !Network` -> sandboxed
   start with (1).

=== The compiler illuminates ===
